{"componentChunkName":"component---src-pages-posts-asciidoc-page-attributes-slug-tsx","path":"/posts/linux-cmd-xxd/","result":{"data":{"asciidoc":{"id":"8d97aaac-8a41-5e99-a4df-464dddafc154","html":"<div id=\"preamble\">\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>xxd 执行 hexdump 或者反向操作。可以通过 xxd 以文本形式编辑二进制文件。</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>测试文件内容：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">$ echo \"中文\" | xxd -p | sed 's/../&amp; /g' &gt; infile\n$ cat infile\ne4 b8 ad e6 96 87 0a</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>sed</code> 每两个字符中间添加一个空格，增加可读性</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>将 hexdump 转换 binary：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">$ xxd -r -p infile outfile\n$ cat outfile\n中文</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>-r</code> 或者 <code>-revert</code> 反向操作，将 hexdump 转换为 binary</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code>-p</code> 连续的 hexdump，无行号以及特定布局</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_和_vim_配合使用\">和 vim 配合使用</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>测试文件内容：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">$ cat infile\n中文</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"olist arabic\">\n<ol class=\"arabic\">\n<li>\n<p>vim 二进制模式编辑文件：</p>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-bash\" data-lang=\"bash\">vim -b infile</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><code>-b</code> 二进制模式</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>将当前内容转换为 hexdump。在 vim COMMAND 模式 中输入如下命令：</p>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-text\" data-lang=\"text\">:%!xxd</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"paragraph\">\n<p>此时文件内容为：</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-text\" data-lang=\"text\">00000000: e4b8 ade6 9687 0a                        .......</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>修改内容：</p>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-text\" data-lang=\"text\">00000000: e696 87e4 b8ad 0a                        .......</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>将 hexdump 转换为二进制。在 vim COMMAND 模式 中输入：</p>\n<div class=\"listingblock\">\n<div class=\"content\">\n<pre class=\"highlight\"><code class=\"language-text\" data-lang=\"text\">:%!xxd -r</code></pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sect1\">\n<h2 id=\"_参考\">参考</h2>\n<div class=\"sectionbody\">\n<div class=\"ulist\">\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7826526/transform-hexadecimal-information-to-binary-using-a-linux-command\" class=\"bare\">https://stackoverflow.com/questions/7826526/transform-hexadecimal-information-to-binary-using-a-linux-command</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/302407/how-to-insert-space-between-individual-digits-in-a-file\" class=\"bare\">https://unix.stackexchange.com/questions/302407/how-to-insert-space-between-individual-digits-in-a-file</a></p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/killkill/archive/2010/06/23/1763785.html\" class=\"bare\">https://www.cnblogs.com/killkill/archive/2010/06/23/1763785.html</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","document":{"title":"Linux 命令：xxd"},"pageAttributes":{"slug":"linux-cmd-xxd","category":"linux"},"revision":{"date":"2023-01-30","number":"1.0"}}},"pageContext":{"id":"8d97aaac-8a41-5e99-a4df-464dddafc154","pageAttributes__slug":"linux-cmd-xxd","__params":{"pageAttributes__slug":"linux-cmd-xxd"}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3143286284"],"slicesMap":{}}